Real HiTOP-PRO Data

ku_hitoppro.Rd

Real responses to items on the HiTOP-PRO from University of Kansas students.

Usage

ku_hitoppro

Format

A tibble with 131 rows and 407 columns.

participant

An anonymized id for each participant

biosex

A factor indicating each participant's biological sex

hitop001 to hitop405

Responses on each item
